There are mutliple input which can help for the Forcasting:
1. Historical Data (Price Open and Close)
2. Divident
3. Split Record
4. Company Ratio
5. Ratio such as P/B & P/E
6. Gordon Growth Model (GGM)
7. Classification Approach - This approach uses outputs in the form of buy (y=+1) and Sell (y=-1) to predict stock movement.
8. use P/E * EPS  = Price.

We need to list the different charts/reports which need to be part of this project.
We also need to decide UI with the diffrent option for user to select and view results. 
